{"tid":1420433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好咁撚小學雞屌尻記者啦","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:15:41.000Z","uid":61824,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1556a1199a619b7a42f544d101c1aca689e950","tid":1420433,"uid":61824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"只不過有一個記者追住其中一條問題要你答已經好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要知道每間報館都會有佢既立場<br />\n而專業既記者可以搵到尖銳既問題等你難答，從而幫到佢既公司<br />\n加上事實上佢地真係無答<br />\n<br />\n記住記者一直以黎都係非常專業咁每日係最前線同大家報道<br />\n千其唔可以見到有人支持示威就打飛機<br />\n有人問啲針對性問題就起底圍屌<br />\n<br />\n最後一定要俾啲掌聲有份搞呢個記者會既巴絲打<br />\n咁短時間做到咁絕對唔容易<br />\n大家要做既係唸唸下次點先可以做到最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"a01fc4902b86a14f8819c921b844a60e9e9ebf5b","tid":1420433,"uid":238688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"係。同埋可以比到市民睇到民間記者會同政府記者會最大既差異，係我地誠意去面對大眾，有問有答。"},{"pid":"87977bd45cd76362652434af0fef3ab28b3fa8c1","tid":1420433,"uid":61824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4933ebb8ab4437de9f72933172a65757ef5585","tid":1420433,"uid":61824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37072aa6b91a6f77c9d409d6e52070e36691166d","tid":1420433,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"同意，push"},{"pid":"37131464f38cb952f6d3999e329f7236c399da0c","tid":1420433,"uid":97190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"有誠意， 第一次算好好"},{"pid":"2736573d8abc69c808a4336379f6d4e1a3006505","tid":1420433,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"有啲咁既濕鳩記者<br />\n先睇得到手足係幾咁勁"},{"pid":"59f6e9105e8bcb48258a770538d6f145609c3910","tid":1420433,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"由尋日傾話要對抗黑警個每日記者會<br />\n今日已經成事，執行力十分勁<br />\n<br />\n記者會巴絲們，你哋做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b450a8a88031ae2f52bdad54d3c3f4bac3bf94","tid":1420433,"uid":61824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2736573d8abc69c808a4336379f6d4e1a3006505","tid":1420433,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"有啲咁既濕鳩記者<br />\n先睇得到手足係幾咁勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"絕對同意 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cd7bdeedee794969483c14210780e36bd8b2c4","tid":1420433,"uid":170255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"其實係屌緊個記者態度衰"},{"pid":"c923ac3d5ade9f092e7bc164a8a801194c739941","tid":1420433,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"係屌柒個記者臨尾扮發脾氣<br />\n借d易想撩慶人<br />\n玩埋d低招柒下柒下<br />\n佢問d屌難問題冇所謂<br />\n真理愈辯愈明"},{"pid":"8ba2c929b0f096407a397e83642509d87fec8919","tid":1420433,"uid":61824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6cd7bdeedee794969483c14210780e36bd8b2c4","tid":1420433,"uid":170255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"其實係屌緊個記者態度衰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"當然明<br />\n但對住呢啲人態度好、答得好反而係助攻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}